      "sentence": "\"The other kids won't let me play with them,\" said Sam.",
      "word_count": 11,
      "approx_duration_sec": 4.68
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "sentence": "\"They say I'm not good enough.\" Lily felt sad for her friend.",
      "word_count": 12,
